  <span id="freeText12656109112920095122" style="display:none">Interesting interpretation of Purgatory. It was certainly a relief after the <a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/15645.Inferno__The_Divine_Comedy__1_" title="Inferno (The Divine Comedy #1) by Dante Alighieri" rel="nofollow noopener">Inferno</a>. I want to read it again before writing a review. On to <a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/32812.Paradiso__The_Divine_Comedy___3_" title="Paradiso (The Divine Comedy, #3) by Dante Alighieri" rel="nofollow noopener">Paradiso</a>.</span>
