<span id="freeTextContainer7291256716752866524"><a href='https://www.goodreads.com/story/show/277496?chapter=6' rel='nofollow noopener'>CDM REVIEW - FINAL: Pooh v Inferno</a><br/><br/>Virgil points out to Pooh where Mary Poppins and Mrs B hang out nowadays - all the rocks were gleamingly clean. <i>ZING</i> The clink of gin bottles with the cackles of laughter indicate a good time was being had by all. Yes, it is a party atomosphere since the Beatles taught the <a href='http://youtu.be/90Li7n56uU8' rel='nofollow noopener'>Cavern how to ::Fab:Four:A:Go:Go::</a><br/><br/>A glimpse through a cavern entrance shows Ophelia trying to confiscate the knitting needles away from Lady M when her back is turned.<br/><br/>Virgil, in his rather sna</span>
  <span id="freeText7291256716752866524" style="display:none"><a href="https://www.goodreads.com/story/show/277496?chapter=6" rel="nofollow noopener">CDM REVIEW - FINAL: Pooh v Inferno</a><br /><br />Virgil points out to Pooh where Mary Poppins and Mrs B hang out nowadays - all the rocks were gleamingly clean. <i>ZING</i> The clink of gin bottles with the cackles of laughter indicate a good time was being had by all. Yes, it is a party atomosphere since the Beatles taught the <a href="http://youtu.be/90Li7n56uU8" rel="nofollow noopener">Cavern how to ::Fab:Four:A:Go:Go::</a><br /><br />A glimpse through a cavern entrance shows Ophelia trying to confiscate the knitting needles away from Lady M when her back is turned.<br /><br />Virgil, in his rather snazzy tour guide uniform, informs Pooh that nobody nowadays is scared of these circular caverns. Sense, or an approximation thereof, has triumphed over superstition; there is no need to feel any despair at all at losing to a location, after all, 100 acre woods is the location that has kept Pooh and his friends enthralled for years.<br /><br />The fun is interrupted for the merest of New York Minutes by Anna Karenina running through with her aptly named 'hystrionic hanky'.<br /><br />Virgil takes Pooh by the hand and they sit on a dolmen side by side. You see Pooh, it is not the winning that is important, all of the contenders get to party here for eternity, <b>so even though technically Dante cannot ever be the loser</b>, everyone is a winner and we get a whole new influx of personalities next year.<br /><br />Bargain!<br /><br /></span>
  <a data-text-id="7291256716752866524" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


