<span id="freeTextContainer220617852235574801">&quot;From those most holy waters<br/>I came away remade, as are new plants<br/>renewed with new-sprung leaves,<br/>pure, and prepared to rise up to the stars.&quot; (Purg. XXXIII. 142-145)</span>
